{"tid":1820913,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"屌 久違既抑鬱病發","createTime":"2020-01-11T22:10:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T13:39:02.000Z","uid":243290,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2cc4bb71dc6d2d0b2ae07d0b11e276d49bcf32d9","tid":1820913,"uid":243290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T22:10:11.000Z","msg":"十二月尾覆診完<br />\n姑娘話我情況好返好多<br />\n可能睇多次就會唔洗再食藥<br />\n但係呢幾日又開始發神經<br />\n除左失眠 又會心口鬱悶無胃口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係好耐無試過呢個感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唉 希望一陣訓醒無事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c61537096c3f6b19a41eb28d58444b599f22eb2","tid":1820913,"uid":243290,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T22:16:47.000Z","msg":"呢幾日爆左幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係因為大家係朋友<br />\n所以講野就會熟 mean<br />\n我份人講野惡 但係無惡意<br />\n但係唔知點解有人會懷疑我係鬧緊人<br />\n朋友之間講笑好正常<br />\n當然過分既可以同我講返<br />\n我願意改<br />\n但係其他人黎一句你走開 你唔好嘈<br />\n加上針對我<br />\n真係聽到覺得好無助"},{"pid":"107cc73de514074826f751a64d7c4333efd32438","tid":1820913,"uid":243290,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T22:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80727345845346bbe9f023042b863528e9c5799c","tid":1820913,"uid":178682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T04:01:26.000Z","msg":"No friend"},{"pid":"4eb658c228ea2b5108478bf3e9d6cb42b1f3acfd","tid":1820913,"uid":225098,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T04:02:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>除咗玩交友App有咩方法識正常男仔？</strong></span>